featured_reviews.review_id: This masjid is very clean. It is easily accessible for the students who study in Mandal college.  Parking is available on the college road. Juma prayers at 1:30Pm.-1:45pm. This masjid is located on a hill. Carpets are clean and dust free. Wazu khana is inside the masjid. Next to the masjid is a government school.
